Class SoftwareStore

java.lang.Object
SoftwareStore
public class SoftwareStore
extends java.lang.Object
Menu-driven program for managing a software store. The system has two types of users: administrators who can update information and users who browse software. The system maintains the information about each software which at least includes name (including version), quantity, and price.
